{"tid":1846761,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今個月1819號去澳門睇sj既絲打入黎好冇阿","createTime":"2020-01-27T17:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T18:48:38.000Z","uid":173321,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7ae77436ba021c11067bc19baaed7a7e2a0d13ae","tid":1846761,"uid":173321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"[代友po] 今個月18,19號去澳門睇super junior 演唱會既人 希望大家可以自隔14日觀察下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有大陸ELF係微博講自己18同19號兩日都有去到sj澳門既con 佢係來自武漢 而且出發之前係醫院做緊最後實習<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢都有提過場內各區分散唔少武漢同湖北ELF  有啲已經主動報左當日演唱會坐/企既位 希望大家注意 直至1月25更新 暫時依家報左位既ELF都聲稱佢地係處於健康狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲係演唱會座位表以供參考:<br />\n20200118<br />\n企位<br />\nA區 x3<br />\nB區x 2<br />\nC區x 10(1名延伸台第１排)<br />\n<br />\n坐位<br />\nA03 x1<br />\nA11 x1<br />\nA14 Row E x1<br />\nA14 Row A x1<br />\nA15 (人數不確定，至少1名)<br />\nA28 x1<br />\nB02 x 1<br />\nB04 x2<br />\nB10 x1<br />\n<br />\n20200119<br />\n企位<br />\nA區x 1<br />\nB區x 1<br />\nC區x 1<br />\nD區x 1<br />\n<br />\n坐位<br />\nA10區x1<br />\nA11區x1<br />\nA12區x1<br />\nB06區x1<br />\nB11區x1<br />\n<br />\n沒有標明日子<br />\n坐位<br />\nA01<br />\nA28 x1<br />\nB10 Row J x1<br />\n資料來源: <a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4464688412664713?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4464688412664713%3F&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5g2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=be513147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/status/4464688412664713?</a><br />\n<br />\n最後希望sj啲oppa同香港ELF健健康康 冇中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/jt9uf2H.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjt9uf2H.png&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5g2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=cdba2c5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/jt9uf2H.png</a><br />\n[/img]<img src=\"http